g>Fixed:<\\/strong> Added back in button styles for the \\\"mark complete\\\" button. They were accidentally removed in the previous version. <em>(plus a few other button tweaks)<\\/em><\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Course Content Tables: Lesson rows now accept the hover background color<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> A few CSS bugs with Uncanny Toolkit\'s [uo_dashboard] shortcode.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.1.1 - July 26, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Dependency check: LearnDash must be activated in order to activate this plugin<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> The plugin now uses any custom labels for Courses, Lessons, Topics or Quizzes set under LearnDash LMS &gt; Settings &gt; Custom Labels<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Cleaner styles for the Uncanny Owl [uo_dashboard] shortcode (but no specific customization options)<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Button styles will now be applied to the :focus state<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Better instructions for activating a license key<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> Course Navigation Widget: Added a little spacing between icon &amp; right edge<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> More specific next\\/previous &amp; \'back to lesson\' button styles to better accommodate more themes<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Folder naming issue<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.1 - July 23, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> 2 new options for hiding elements on the [ld_profile] shortcode output<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> 17 new options for designing the Course Navigation Widget, including:\\n<ul>\\n<li>auto-expand all lessons\\/topics<\\/li>\\n<li>lesson\\/topic\\/quiz indentation<\\/li>\\n<li>text color, hover color, hover background color, border &amp; border colors<\\/li>\\n<li>custom spacing between each lesson<\\/li>\\n<li>remove (or customize) the line separators between topics &amp; quizzes<\\/li>\\n<li>remove the \\\"back to [course]\\\" link<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.0 - June 26, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Initial release<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n\"]}\";}',	'no'),
