ange border, background &amp; text color for all 3 types of LearnDash alerts<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>New:<\\/strong> Alerts: Remove alert icons<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>New:<\\/strong> Alerts: Set a border width for all alerts<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fix:<\\/strong> Quiz buttons now properly inherit your button styles<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fix:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Alert icon position on smaller screens<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.1 - Released Jun 26, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<p><strong>Ribbon colors are back!<\\/strong> Thank you for the feedback. Keep it coming.<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Course Grid: Ribbon background &amp; text colors for default, enrolled, free &amp; custom ribbons<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fix:<\\/strong> When disabling expand\\/collapse on course content lists, it was also being disabled on the Profile<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.0.1 - Released Jun 24, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<p>I\'ve heard your feedback and will be adding back the ability to customize course grid ribbon colors in the next release (~5-8 days).<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Fix:<\\/strong> Legacy: Button styles were not being properly applied when using the \\\"Legacy\\\" template<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fix:<\\/strong> Add space for \\\"Download Certificate\\\" button icon, and other small tweaks to buttons within alerts<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Alerts: Vertically center all icons<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Focus Mode: Small improvements to spacing of username in header<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Improved styles when \\\"Mark Complete\\\" button is disabled<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Tweak:<\\/strong> More specific button style to avoid some theme conflicts with link colors<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>2.0 - Released Jun 22, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>IMPORTANT:<\\/strong>\\u00a0LearnDash\'s color settings must be disabled for our plugin\'s colors to take effect<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Now compatible with the LearnDash 3.0 Active Template<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> New style options for focus mode, tooltips, course content, profile &amp; more<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Tons of updated styles for quizzes (no customization; just improved styles)<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> Options are now saved globally. Styles remain in place even when you switch themes.<\\/li>\\n<li>Official videos &amp; explanations of all settings will be released soon<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.7.3 - Released Mar 23, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> Course Grid: Buttons are now displayed at the very bottom of each grid item<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.7.2 - Released Mar 11, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Added a min-width of 45px to the number column in the course content table. This accounts for up to 999 items on most devices &amp; themes, without forcing the number to a new line.<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Course Grid: Inline &amp; full-width buttons both work again<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.7.1 - Released Feb 8, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Bug that was preventing administrators from accessing a user\'s \\\"Edit Profile\\\" page in the admin area<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.7 - Released Jan 23, 2019<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Set a custom URL for\\u00a0the \\\"Edit Profile\\\" link when using the [ld_profile] shortcode<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Hide \\\"Enrolled Course Points\\\" in the [ld_profile] shortcode<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> Small spacing adjustment to the list count numbers in course content tables<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> Adjusted alignment of quiz headings when quizzes are displayed in the [ld_profile]\\u00a0shortcode<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.6.3 - Released Dec 13, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Boss. Theme: We are now compatible with the Boss. theme, but you need to deactivate the \\\"Boss for LearnDash\\\" plugin.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.6.2 - Released Dec 11, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Twenty Nineteen: Updated a few styles for compatibility with the Twenty Nineteen theme<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Confirmed compatibility with WordPress 5.0, Gutenberg and the Classic Editor plugin<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.6.1 - Released Nov 2, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> .pot file so Customizer text can be properly translated<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Woffice: Tweaked a few styles for compatibility with the Woffice theme from Alkalab<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.6 - Released Oct 31, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> OceanWP: Ensured compatibility with OceanWP\'s new LearnDash styles<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> More specific button style for \\\"back to lesson\\\" button<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Dev:<\\/strong> Bug fix: Prefix a function name to avoid potential conflicts<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.5.7 - Released Oct 16, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Customizer options now have proper text domain, making them ready for translation<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Course Grid: Columns weren\'t working properly with some page builders<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Course Grid: Some styles weren\'t being applied when Course Grid shortcode was used with page builders<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Divi: Fixed issue with Course Grid item border styles<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.5.6 - Released Oct 15, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Primary Button colors now applied to buttons when using the [learndash_payment_buttons] shortcode<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> Course Grid column styles updated to be compatible with Course Grid version 1.5.1<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Divi: Course category selector background color was not being applied<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.5.5 - Released Oct 14, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Hide \\\"Course Content\\\" header text<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Hide \\\"Edit Profile\\\" link when using the [ld_profile] shortcode<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Added space between Topic table &amp; \\\"Mark Complete\\\" button<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Divi: Course Grid ribbon styles were not being applied<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.5.4 - Released Sep 18, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Course Grid: CSS was updated for better compatibility with the Divi plugin<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> A few small CSS optimizations so the plugin uses less code<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.5.3 - Released Sep 13, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Some course grid styles are now more specific so they override default styles<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.5.2 - Released Sep 12, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Quiz timer bar now accepts striped settings (if selected for the progress bar)<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> \\\"Sending\\\" quiz bar was flowing outside of the content area in some cases (depending on progress bar settings)<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.5.1 - Released Sep 11, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Added a small change for course grid columns on some themes that also use Bootstrap (ex: Uncode)<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> Quiz time limit bar now uses the same height, background color &amp; border radius as defined for the progress bar<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Button Styles: \\\"Print Your Certificate\\\", as well as several other quiz-related buttons, now correctly inherit the button styles (\\\"Click Here to Continue\\\", \\\"Finish Quiz\\\", \\\"Restart Quiz\\\")<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.5 - Released Sep 8, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> 24 new options for the LearnDash Course Grid add-on<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Better styles for the \\\"not available\\\" message when a lesson is scheduled for a later date<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> Force \\\"Mark Complete\\\" buttons to have a hand pointer on hover<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> Updated topic dots to use CSS background colors instead of images<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Removed:<\\/strong> Animation for \\\"sending quiz...\\\" progress bar. It was preventing the quiz bar from completely finishing in some implementations.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.4 - August 19, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Course Content Tables: Table border width &amp; color can now be customized<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Course Content Tables: Small, medium or large padding can be applied to each row<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Course Navigation Widget: Small, medium or large padding can be applied to each row<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Course Content Tables: Border radius wasn\'t being properly applied<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.3.2 - August 17, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Link colors were not being applied to Expand\\/Collapse, \\\"back to course\\\" link in Course Nav Widget, and a few other spots<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Adjusted styles on progress bars and links within course content tables for better compatibility with Astra Pro<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Course content link styles now fully apply to Uncanny Toolkit\'s [uo_dashboard] shortcode<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.3.1 - August 8, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong>\\u00a0Quiz answer background colors were the same as text color, making them illegible<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Changed:<\\/strong> A few other CSS tweaks to make sure correct\\/incorrect colors were applied to quiz elements appropriately<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.3 - August 8, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Completely revamped the quiz styles, including the quiz statistics popup<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Option to hide status checkmarks on Course Content lists<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Option to hide status checkmarks on Course Navigation Widget<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Status icons now appear in course content lists when using Divi LearnDash Kit<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> If expand\\/collapse was disabled for the course navigation widget, it was also applying to the course content lists<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.2.1 - August 2, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Compatibility:<\\/strong> Now compatible with the Astra theme<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> A few small changes to button styles for better overall theme compatibility<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p><strong>1.2 - July 31, 2018<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Button Border Radius<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Course Navigation Widget: Move \\\"Return to Course\\\" link to the top<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Progress Bar: Display \'X out of Y steps completed\' above or below the bar<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Added:<\\/strong> Videos using Video Progression are now responsive by default<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Added back in button styles for the \\\"mark complete\\\" button. They were accidentally removed in the previous version. <em>(plus a few other button tweaks)<\\/em><\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> Course Content Tables: Lesson rows now accept the hover background color<\\/li>\\n<li><strong>Fixed:<\\/strong> A few CSS bugs with Uncanny Toolkit\'s [uo_dashboard] shortcode.<